entry.def: Your chest is the top  part of the front of your body where your ribs, lungs, and heart are.

example.ex: He crossed his arms over his chest...
He was shot in the chest...

entry.def: A chest is a large, heavy box used for storing things.

example.ex: At the very bottom of the chest were his carving tools.
example.tran: 箱子最底下是他的雕刻工具。

entry.tran: 倾诉胸中的不快;吐苦水
entry.def: If you get something off your chest, you talk about something that has been worrying you.
